{"tid":2396410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被控大叫「死黑警」 手足憑手機拍片脫罪","createTime":"2021-02-05T14:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T15:36:38.000Z","uid":285248,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aaef8d6d7b7e093e833a72ea54874fbb6f9c64c3","tid":2396410,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"全世界學拍片自救呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//2019年11月18日理工大學衝突期間，一名25歲青年在附近用手機進行拍攝，期間被指高呼「死黑警」等辱警語句，引起在場人士起哄。他早前否認一項在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為罪，經審訊後今日（5日）在九龍城法院被裁定罪名不成立。裁判官鄭念慈接納被告拍攝的手機片段顯示，他當時無說出相關的辱警說話，警員證人的證供並不可靠，故判他脫罪。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpNmtqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpNmtqv.jpg&h=2fa1b71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/beizhimajingraoluanzhixu-qingnianpingshoujizipaipiantuozui-110739189.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fbeizhimajingraoluanzhixu-qingnianpingshoujizipaipiantuozui-110739189.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=b64a6f90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/beizhimajingraoluanzhixu-qingnianpingshoujizipaipiantuozui-110739189.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk</a>"},{"pid":"60ae08457d47dee76762bfccd715ea0e38f0d47a","tid":2396410,"uid":345689,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"警員証供不可靠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩個官肯接納條片做呈堂証供"},{"pid":"630d1004ff67dbaf7964687d602bc73b48ec7fec","tid":2396410,"uid":164761,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"狗官黎，今次屈唔到先逼於無奈"},{"pid":"d7f1fad81287207ee95223f35db4dd586e48a0bc","tid":2396410,"uid":275243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-0